ą odnajdą Państwo rozwiązanie, które będzie spełniało wszystkie wymagania, zarówno finansowe jak i użytkowe.";s:17:"short_description";s:217:"Projekty domów dla rodzin 2+3 z trójką dzieci lub rodzin, które planują powiększenie. Wygodne domy dla 5 osobowej rodziny, w których każdy znajdzie swoje miejsce, a zarazem nikt nie będzie czuł się samotny.";s:12:"project_list";s:1508:"1793,1739,1735,1728,1725,1375,1580,1747,1540,1296,1683,1344,1560,1544,1541,1294,1559,1639,1340,1734,1796,1724,1614,1274,1665,1330,1749,1233,909,1732,1182,1440,1662,834,1532,1242,1079,1595,1726,1714,1795,1413,1504,1106,1669,1685,134,1756,1475,1698,775,399,1582,1496,1272,1376,1434,1391,1383,1088,1502,841,1331,1471,1086,1292,1313,1372,1218,1641,1204,1589,1231,1507,1320,864,1140,1581,1149,1788,1459,1657,1046,1192,1229,1152,1030,1150,1084,1655,1498,585,1533,1360,1421,1315,1723,1603,780,1422,863,1501,1147,697,1324,902,644,1356,1143,1263,1116,1384,1488,776,1099,1386,842,1174,1185,1301,1213,1188,1190,1566,1178,1180,1197,1232,391,1077,1096,318,1059,1066,1160,1267,1132,1424,1367,1163,1176,1155,1305,713,1304,1028,980,402,604,938,1453,1236,733,384,443,52,501,63,314,406,1051,270,135,1107,1081,711,429,856,830,1167,1184,1170,1216,490,61,920,1514,852,592,1109,1052,738,577,516,1065,1511,916,1515,628,560,1114,991,1142,1113,1072,1063,687,792,636,404,1136,798,735,1001,1158,861,630,1068,850,736,594,1006,1003,1102,669,1223,989,1221,786,762,853,727,534,1039,940,1186,911,739,710,1138,1148,985,1044,919,889,891,676,395,1151,1021,981,706,723,1056,709,744,580,1020,921,855,742,671,614,607,397,293,239,1161,1117,1101,1228,1156,708,249,993,956,963,1029,1033,1049,1024,226,209,137,1013,790,751,732,712,439,1119,584,1009,848,846,810,769,734,716,678,641,640,934,765,698,1130,497,983,917,761,741,702,149,1144,737,631,951,922,937,933,847,779,773,715,717,718,707,724,643,608,609,602,586,615,579,559,543,536,520,494,486,385,142";s:20:"project_list_by_area";s:1508:"318,1657,1655,630,615,270,1119,981,1106,1589,1242,134,644,534,1272,142,61,11